# CRUD Patterns (Inboxes reference implementation)

## Controller

- `before_action :set_resource` for all member actions
- On failure: `render :new/:edit, status: :unprocessable_entity`
- On success: `redirect_to @resource, notice: "Resource was successfully created/updated."`
- Private `set_resource` (finds by `params[:id]`) and `resource_params` (strong params)
- For JSON columns: expose virtual `*_text` attributes; populate in `new`/`edit` with `JSON.pretty_generate`

```ruby
# ✅ GOOD
def create
  @inbox = Inbox.new(inbox_params)
  if @inbox.save
    redirect_to @inbox, notice: "Inbox was successfully created."
  else
    render :new, status: :unprocessable_entity
  end
end
```

## Index View

- Root: `<div data-controller="keyboard-shortcuts">`
- Default: list (table), optional grid via `?view=grid`
- Render `'header'` and `'filter_tabs'` partials at the top
- Bulk select: `data-bulk-actions-target="checkbox"`, `data-action="change->bulk-actions#updateActions"`
- Empty state: centered SVG + `<h3>` + `<p>` inside `rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 py-16 text-center`
- End of template: `<turbo-frame id="modal"></turbo-frame>`

## Show View

- Root: `<div data-controller="keyboard-shortcuts">`
- Header row: back link with `u` shortcut, resource title, Edit button (`e`), Delete `button_to` (red)
- Details card: `<dl class="divide-y divide-gray-100">` with `<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 px-6 py-4">` rows
- JSON display: `<pre class="overflow-auto rounded-md bg-gray-50 p-4 font-mono text-xs text-gray-800 leading-relaxed max-h-80"><%= JSON.pretty_generate(resource.field || {}) %></pre>`

## New / Edit Views

- Breadcrumb back-link at top (edit wraps in `data-controller="keyboard-shortcuts"`)
- Render form inside: `<div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">`

## Form Partial

Error banner (always first):
```erb
<% if resource.errors.any? %>
  <div class="rounded-md bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-4">
    <!-- SVG icon + pluralize(count, 'error') heading + ul of full_messages -->
  </div>
<% end %>
```

Standard input class:
```
block w-full rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 placeholder-gray-400 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500
```

Submit button:
```
inline-flex justify-center rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600 transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer
```

- Submit label: `resource.persisted? ? 'Update Resource' : 'Create Resource'`
- Cancel link: `resource.persisted? ? resource : resources_path`

## Tailwind Component Tokens

| Component | Classes |
|-----------|---------|
| Card | `rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm` |
| Card section header | `border-b border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 px-6 py-3` |
| Badge base | `inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium` |
| Status: unprocessed | `bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700` |
| Status: processed / success | `bg-green-100 text-green-700` |
| Status: archived / neutral | `bg-gray-100 text-gray-600` |
| Secondary button | `inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50` |
| Danger button | `inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-red-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-red-700 ring-1 ring-inset ring-red-200 hover:bg-red-100` |

## Keyboard Shortcuts

Root element: `data-controller="keyboard-shortcuts"`

Annotate links with:
```erb
data: { keyboard_shortcuts_target: "trigger", keyboard_shortcuts_key: "e" }
```

Show hint: `<kbd class="rounded border border-gray-200 bg-gray-100 px-1 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs font-normal text-gray-400">e</kbd>`

Standard shortcuts: `n` new, `e` edit, `u` back, `p` process, `a` archive, `d` delete, `?` help overlay.
